column5: The deal is done, we are ready to ship the latest and greatest in Walleye Central gear. These decals are super quality, made by our oun community member Rob Stratton. These will look great on your truck, car, or boat, and will tell the world you are a Walleye Central community member. All you have to do to get yours is email me(addy at the bottom of the page)with your request, I will give you the snail mail addy to send your check or money order(made out to Walleye Central.
